(227, 36, 1, 1, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO1 (1.0) as it directly requires applying principles of engineering, science, and mathematics to solve complex problems. It also maps strongly to PLO2 (0.8) and PLO6 (0.8) as design and experimentation both require deep subject matter knowledge.', '', '2026-02-20 13:29:03', '2026-02-20 13:29:03'),
(228, 36, 1, 2, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO1 (1.0) as formulating and solving complex engineering problems is the essence of critical thinking in this field. It also maps strongly to PLO2 (0.8) and PLO6 (0.8) as design and experimentation require critical evaluation and analysis.', '', '2026-02-20 13:29:03', '2026-02-20 13:29:03'),
(229, 36, 1, 3, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO1 (1.0) as it is explicitly about solving complex engineering problems. It also maps strongly to PLO2 (0.8) and PLO6 (0.8) as design and experimentation are core problem-solving activities.', '', '2026-02-20 13:29:03', '2026-02-20 13:29:03'),
