(302, 33, 5, 17, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO2 (1.0) as engineering design is an inherently creative and innovative process. It also maps moderately to PLO1 (0.5), PLO6 (0.5), and PLO7 (0.5) as problem-solving, experimentation, and acquiring new knowledge all involve creativity.', '', '2026-02-20 13:31:59', '2026-02-20 13:31:59'),
(303, 33, 5, 18, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO5 (1.0) as it is explicitly about functioning effectively on a team. It also maps strongly to PLO3 (0.8) as collaboration requires effective communication.', '', '2026-02-20 13:31:59', '2026-02-20 13:31:59'),
(304, 33, 5, 19, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO5 (1.0) as teamwork involves planning tasks and meeting objectives, which are management functions. It also maps moderately to PLO2 (0.5) as the design process requires management.', '', '2026-02-20 13:31:59', '2026-02-20 13:31:59'),
(305, 33, 5, 20, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO5 (1.0) as teamwork requires strong interpersonal skills. It also maps strongly to PLO3 (0.8) as effective communication is a key interpersonal skill.', '', '2026-02-20 13:31:59', '2026-02-20 13:31:59'),
(306, 33, 5, 21, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO5 (1.0) as it explicitly includes providing leadership within a team. It also maps moderately to PLO2 (0.5), PLO4 (0.5), and PLO7 (0.5) as design, ethical responsibility, and lifelong learning all provide opportunities for leadership.', '', '2026-02-20 13:31:59', '2026-02-20 13:31:59'),
(307, 25, 1, 1, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO1 (1.0) as it directly requires applying key theories and concepts of the subject matter. It also maps moderately to PLO2 (0.8) since planning effective instruction requires mastery of content. Lower mappings to PLO3 (0.5), PLO4 (0.5), PLO5 (0.5), and PLO6 (0.5) reflect that these outcomes require some subject knowledge but are not primarily focused on content mastery.', '', '2026-02-20 13:32:43', '2026-02-20 13:32:43'),
(308, 25, 1, 2, 'This competency maps most strongly to PLO3 (1.0) as using technology in instructionally powerful ways requires critical evaluation of tools and their applications. It also maps strongly to PLO2 (0.8) and PLO6 (0.8) as planning instruction and engaging in scholarly inquiry both demand critical thinking. Moderate mappings to PLO1 (0.5), PLO4 (0.5), and PLO5 (0.5) reflect that these outcomes involve critical thinking but to a lesser degree.', '', '2026-02-20 13:32:43', '2026-02-20 13:32:43'),
(309, 25, 1, 3, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO5 (1.0) as arriving at data-informed decisions is fundamentally a problem-solving process. It also maps strongly to PLO4 (0.8) and PLO6 (0.8) as addressing diversity and conducting research both involve solving complex problems. Moderate mappings to PLO2 (0.5), PLO3 (0.5), and PLO8 (0.5) indicate these outcomes require problem-solving but as a supporting skill.', '', '2026-02-20 13:32:43', '2026-02-20 13:32:43'),
(310, 25, 1, 4, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO6 (1.0) as scholarly inquiry is the direct manifestation of research skills. It also maps strongly to PLO8 (0.8) since leading positive change requires innovative and adaptive thinking. Lower mappings to PLO2 (0.2), PLO3 (0.2), PLO4 (0.2), and PLO5 (0.2) reflect minimal research components in these outcomes.', '', '2026-02-20 13:32:43', '2026-02-20 13:32:43'),
(311, 25, 2, 5, 'This competency maps moderately to PLO6 (0.5) and PLO8 (0.5) as scholarly inquiry and leading change both require self-reflection and awareness of one\'s strengths and limitations. Minimal mappings (0.2) to PLO2, PLO4, PLO5, and PLO7 indicate some self-awareness is needed but not central to these outcomes.', '', '2026-02-20 13:32:43', '2026-02-20 13:32:43'),
(312, 25, 2, 6, 'This competency maps strongly to PLO4 (0.8) and PLO8 (0.8) as fostering learning for diverse students and leading change both require significant adaptability. Moderate mappings to PLO2 (0.5), PLO3 (0.5), PLO5 (0.5), and PLO6 (0.5) reflect that these outcomes benefit from adaptability but don\'t primarily focus on it.', '', '2026-02-20 13:32:43', '2026-02-20 13:32:43'),
(313, 25, 2, 7, 'This competency maps strongly across multiple PLOs: PLO2 (0.8), PLO4 (0.8), PLO5 (0.8), PLO6 (0.8), and PLO8 (0.8) as planning instruction, addressing diversity, making data-informed decisions, conducting research, and leading change all require adaptive thinking. Moderate mappings to PLO1 (0.5) and PLO3 (0.5) indicate these outcomes involve some adaptive thinking.', '', '2026-02-20 13:32:43', '2026-02-20 13:32:43'),
(314, 25, 2, 8, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO6 (1.0) as actively engaging in scholarship directly embodies the desire for continuous learning. It also maps strongly to PLO8 (0.8) since leading positive change requires ongoing professional development. Moderate mappings to PLO2 (0.5), PLO4 (0.5), PLO5 (0.5), and PLO7 (0.5) reflect that these outcomes support but don\'t directly emphasize life-long learning.', '', '2026-02-20 13:32:43', '2026-02-20 13:32:43'),
(315, 25, 3, 9, 'This competency maps most strongly to PLO4 (0.8) as fostering successful learning for all students requires cultural awareness and sensitivity. Minimal mappings (0.2) to PLO2, PLO6, PLO7, and PLO8 indicate limited cultural components in these outcomes.', '', '2026-02-20 13:32:43', '2026-02-20 13:32:43'),
(316, 25, 3, 10, 'This competency maps strongly across most PLOs: PLO1 (0.8), PLO2 (0.8), PLO4 (0.8), and PLO6 (0.8) as applying concepts, planning instruction, addressing diversity, and conducting research all require strong communication. Moderate mappings to PLO3 (0.5), PLO5 (0.5), and PLO8 (0.5) reflect communication as a supporting skill.', '', '2026-02-20 13:32:43', '2026-02-20 13:32:43'),
(317, 25, 3, 11, 'This competency maps most strongly to PLO4 (0.8) as addressing individual differences requires awareness of diverse contexts and issues. It also maps moderately to PLO5 (0.5), PLO6 (0.5), PLO7 (0.5), and PLO8 (0.5) as these outcomes benefit from contextual awareness.', '', '2026-02-20 13:32:43', '2026-02-20 13:32:43'),
(318, 25, 4, 12, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO7 (1.0) as applying professional ethics directly embodies cultural and religious identity in educational contexts. It also maps strongly to PLO4 (0.8) as fostering learning for all students requires respect for identity and values. Moderate mapping to PLO8 (0.5) and minimal mappings to other PLOs reflect varying degrees of identity-related components.', '', '2026-02-20 13:32:43', '2026-02-20 13:32:43'),
(319, 25, 4, 13, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO4 (1.0) as fostering successful learning for all students by addressing individual differences is the direct manifestation of embracing diversity. It also maps strongly to PLO8 (0.8) as leading positive change requires valuing diverse perspectives. Moderate mappings to PLO1 (0.5), PLO2 (0.5), PLO5 (0.5), PLO6 (0.5), and PLO7 (0.5) indicate these outcomes involve diversity considerations.', '', '2026-02-20 13:32:43', '2026-02-20 13:32:43'),
(320, 25, 4, 14, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO7 (1.0) as applying professional ethics is the direct expression of ethical conduct. It also maps strongly to PLO1 (0.8), PLO4 (0.8), and PLO6 (0.8) as these outcomes require adherence to professional standards. Moderate mappings to PLO2 (0.5) and PLO8 (0.5) reflect ethical considerations in these areas.', '', '2026-02-20 13:32:43', '2026-02-20 13:32:43'),
(321, 25, 4, 15, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO7 (1.0) and PLO8 (0.8) as applying ethics and leading change both involve civic engagement and social responsibility. It also maps strongly to PLO4 (0.8) as addressing diversity requires civic awareness. Moderate mappings to PLO5 (0.5) and PLO6 (0.5) indicate some civic awareness components.', '', '2026-02-20 13:32:43', '2026-02-20 13:32:43'),
(322, 25, 5, 17, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO6 (0.8) and PLO8 (0.8) as scholarly inquiry and leading positive change both require creative and innovative approaches. Moderate mapping to PLO3 (0.5) reflects the creative use of technology.', '', '2026-02-20 13:32:43', '2026-02-20 13:32:43'),
(323, 25, 5, 18, 'This competency maps most strongly to PLO4 (0.8) and PLO8 (0.8) as addressing diversity and leading change both require collaboration with diverse stakeholders. Moderate mappings to PLO2 (0.5) reflect collaborative aspects in planning instruction.', '', '2026-02-20 13:32:43', '2026-02-20 13:32:43'),
(324, 25, 5, 19, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO8 (0.8) as leading positive change requires management skills. It also maps moderately to PLO5 (0.5) as data-informed decision-making involves resource management.', '', '2026-02-20 13:32:43', '2026-02-20 13:32:43'),
(325, 25, 5, 20, 'This competency maps most strongly to PLO4 (0.8) as fostering learning for diverse students requires strong interpersonal skills. It also maps moderately to PLO1 (0.5) and PLO2 (0.5) as these outcomes involve working with others.', '', '2026-02-20 13:32:43', '2026-02-20 13:32:43'),
(326, 25, 5, 21, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO8 (1.0) as leading positive change in education is the direct manifestation of leadership. Minimal mappings (0.2) to other PLOs indicate that while some leadership may be involved, it is not a primary focus of those outcomes.', '', '2026-02-20 13:32:43', '2026-02-20 13:32:43');
INSERT INTO `justifications` (`id`, `programId`, `gaId`, `competencyId`, `textEn`, `textAr`, `createdAt`, `updatedAt`) VALUES
