(367, 27, 1, 1, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO1 (1.0) as it directly requires applying key theories and concepts of the subject matter. It also maps moderately to PLO2 (0.8) since planning effective instruction requires mastery of content. Lower mappings to PLO3 (0.5), PLO4 (0.5), PLO5 (0.5), and PLO6 (0.5) reflect that these outcomes require some subject knowledge but are not primarily focused on content mastery.', '', '2026-02-20 13:33:57', '2026-02-20 13:33:57'),
(368, 27, 1, 2, 'This competency maps most strongly to PLO3 (1.0) as using technology in instructionally powerful ways requires critical evaluation of tools and their applications. It also maps strongly to PLO2 (0.8) and PLO6 (0.8) as planning instruction and engaging in scholarly inquiry both demand critical thinking. Moderate mappings to PLO1 (0.5), PLO4 (0.5), and PLO5 (0.5) reflect that these outcomes involve critical thinking but to a lesser degree.', '', '2026-02-20 13:33:57', '2026-02-20 13:33:57'),
(369, 27, 1, 3, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO5 (1.0) as arriving at data-informed decisions is fundamentally a problem-solving process. It also maps strongly to PLO4 (0.8) and PLO6 (0.8) as addressing diversity and conducting research both involve solving complex problems. Moderate mappings to PLO2 (0.5), PLO3 (0.5), and PLO8 (0.5) indicate these outcomes require problem-solving but as a supporting skill.', '', '2026-02-20 13:33:57', '2026-02-20 13:33:57'),
(370, 27, 1, 4, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO6 (1.0) as scholarly inquiry is the direct manifestation of research skills. It also maps strongly to PLO8 (0.8) since leading positive change requires innovative and adaptive thinking. Lower mappings to PLO2 (0.2), PLO3 (0.2), PLO4 (0.2), and PLO5 (0.2) reflect minimal research components in these outcomes.', '', '2026-02-20 13:33:57', '2026-02-20 13:33:57'),
(371, 27, 2, 5, 'This competency maps moderately to PLO6 (0.5) and PLO8 (0.5) as scholarly inquiry and leading change both require self-reflection and awareness of one\'s strengths and limitations. Minimal mappings (0.2) to PLO2, PLO4, PLO5, and PLO7 indicate some self-awareness is needed but not central to these outcomes.', '', '2026-02-20 13:33:57', '2026-02-20 13:33:57'),
(372, 27, 2, 6, 'This competency maps strongly to PLO4 (0.8) and PLO8 (0.8) as fostering learning for diverse students and leading change both require significant adaptability. Moderate mappings to PLO2 (0.5), PLO3 (0.5), PLO5 (0.5), and PLO6 (0.5) reflect that these outcomes benefit from adaptability but don\'t primarily focus on it.', '', '2026-02-20 13:33:57', '2026-02-20 13:33:57'),
(373, 27, 2, 7, 'This competency maps strongly across multiple PLOs: PLO2 (0.8), PLO4 (0.8), PLO5 (0.8), PLO6 (0.8), and PLO8 (0.8) as planning instruction, addressing diversity, making data-informed decisions, conducting research, and leading change all require adaptive thinking. Moderate mappings to PLO1 (0.5) and PLO3 (0.5) indicate these outcomes involve some adaptive thinking.', '', '2026-02-20 13:33:57', '2026-02-20 13:33:57'),
(374, 27, 2, 8, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO6 (1.0) as actively engaging in scholarship directly embodies the desire for continuous learning. It also maps strongly to PLO8 (0.8) since leading positive change requires ongoing professional development. Moderate mappings to PLO2 (0.5), PLO4 (0.5), PLO5 (0.5), and PLO7 (0.5) reflect that these outcomes support but don\'t directly emphasize life-long learning.', '', '2026-02-20 13:33:57', '2026-02-20 13:33:57'),
(375, 27, 3, 9, 'This competency maps most strongly to PLO4 (0.8) as fostering successful learning for all students requires cultural awareness and sensitivity. Minimal mappings (0.2) to PLO2, PLO6, PLO7, and PLO8 indicate limited cultural components in these outcomes.', '', '2026-02-20 13:33:57', '2026-02-20 13:33:57'),
(376, 27, 3, 10, 'This competency maps strongly across most PLOs: PLO1 (0.8), PLO2 (0.8), PLO4 (0.8), and PLO6 (0.8) as applying concepts, planning instruction, addressing diversity, and conducting research all require strong communication. Moderate mappings to PLO3 (0.5), PLO5 (0.5), and PLO8 (0.5) reflect communication as a supporting skill.', '', '2026-02-20 13:33:57', '2026-02-20 13:33:57'),
(377, 27, 3, 11, 'This competency maps most strongly to PLO4 (0.8) as addressing individual differences requires awareness of diverse contexts and issues. It also maps moderately to PLO5 (0.5), PLO6 (0.5), PLO7 (0.5), and PLO8 (0.5) as these outcomes benefit from contextual awareness.', '', '2026-02-20 13:33:57', '2026-02-20 13:33:57'),
(378, 27, 4, 12, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO7 (1.0) as applying professional ethics directly embodies cultural and religious identity in educational contexts. It also maps strongly to PLO4 (0.8) as fostering learning for all students requires respect for identity and values. Moderate mapping to PLO8 (0.5) and minimal mappings to other PLOs reflect varying degrees of identity-related components.', '', '2026-02-20 13:33:57', '2026-02-20 13:33:57'),
(379, 27, 4, 13, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO4 (1.0) as fostering successful learning for all students by addressing individual differences is the direct manifestation of embracing diversity. It also maps strongly to PLO8 (0.8) as leading positive change requires valuing diverse perspectives. Moderate mappings to PLO1 (0.5), PLO2 (0.5), PLO5 (0.5), PLO6 (0.5), and PLO7 (0.5) indicate these outcomes involve diversity considerations.', '', '2026-02-20 13:33:57', '2026-02-20 13:33:57'),
(380, 27, 4, 14, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO7 (1.0) as applying professional ethics is the direct expression of ethical conduct. It also maps strongly to PLO1 (0.8), PLO4 (0.8), and PLO6 (0.8) as these outcomes require adherence to professional standards. Moderate mappings to PLO2 (0.5) and PLO8 (0.5) reflect ethical considerations in these areas.', '', '2026-02-20 13:33:57', '2026-02-20 13:33:57'),
(381, 27, 4, 15, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO7 (1.0) and PLO8 (0.8) as applying ethics and leading change both involve civic engagement and social responsibility. It also maps strongly to PLO4 (0.8) as addressing diversity requires civic awareness. Moderate mappings to PLO5 (0.5) and PLO6 (0.5) indicate some civic awareness components.', '', '2026-02-20 13:33:57', '2026-02-20 13:33:57'),
(382, 27, 5, 17, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO6 (0.8) and PLO8 (0.8) as scholarly inquiry and leading positive change both require creative and innovative approaches. Moderate mapping to PLO3 (0.5) reflects the creative use of technology.', '', '2026-02-20 13:33:57', '2026-02-20 13:33:57'),
(383, 27, 5, 18, 'This competency maps most strongly to PLO4 (0.8) and PLO8 (0.8) as addressing diversity and leading change both require collaboration with diverse stakeholders. Moderate mappings to PLO2 (0.5) reflect collaborative aspects in planning instruction.', '', '2026-02-20 13:33:57', '2026-02-20 13:33:57'),
(384, 27, 5, 19, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO8 (0.8) as leading positive change requires management skills. It also maps moderately to PLO5 (0.5) as data-informed decision-making involves resource management.', '', '2026-02-20 13:33:57', '2026-02-20 13:33:57'),
(385, 27, 5, 20, 'This competency maps most strongly to PLO4 (0.8) as fostering learning for diverse students requires strong interpersonal skills. It also maps moderately to PLO1 (0.5) and PLO2 (0.5) as these outcomes involve working with others.', '', '2026-02-20 13:33:57', '2026-02-20 13:33:57'),
(386, 27, 5, 21, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO8 (1.0) as leading positive change in education is the direct manifestation of leadership. Minimal mappings (0.2) to other PLOs indicate that while some leadership may be involved, it is not a primary focus of those outcomes.', '', '2026-02-20 13:33:57', '2026-02-20 13:33:57'),
(387, 44, 1, 1, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO2 (1.0) as it is explicitly about knowledge for practice. It also maps strongly to PLO1 (0.8) as patient care requires deep subject matter knowledge.', '', '2026-02-20 13:34:37', '2026-02-20 13:34:37'),
(388, 44, 1, 2, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO1 (0.8), PLO2 (0.8), and PLO3 (0.8) as patient care, knowledge application, and evidence-based practice all require significant critical thinking.', '', '2026-02-20 13:34:37', '2026-02-20 13:34:37'),
(389, 44, 1, 3, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO1 (1.0) as it is explicitly about formulating management strategies for patients, which is a core problem-solving activity. It also maps strongly to PLO2 (0.8), PLO3 (0.8), and PLO6 (0.8).', '', '2026-02-20 13:34:37', '2026-02-20 13:34:37'),
(390, 44, 1, 4, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO3 (1.0) as it is explicitly about evidence-based practice and lifelong learning, which includes research skills.', '', '2026-02-20 13:34:37', '2026-02-20 13:34:37'),
(391, 44, 2, 5, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO5 (0.8) as professionalism includes recognizing one\'s own limitations and continuously improving. It also maps moderately across PLO1, PLO3, and PLO4 (0.5).', '', '2026-02-20 13:34:37', '2026-02-20 13:34:37'),
(392, 44, 2, 6, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO3 (0.8) as lifelong learning is the key to adaptability in the medical field. It also maps moderately across PLO1, PLO4, PLO5, and PLO6 (0.5).', '', '2026-02-20 13:34:37', '2026-02-20 13:34:37'),
(393, 44, 2, 7, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO1 (0.8) and PLO3 (0.8) as both patient care and evidence-based practice require adaptive thinking to respond to new information and patient conditions.', '', '2026-02-20 13:34:37', '2026-02-20 13:34:37'),
(394, 44, 2, 8, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO3 (1.0) as it is explicitly about lifelong learning.', '', '2026-02-20 13:34:37', '2026-02-20 13:34:37'),
(395, 44, 3, 9, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO1 (0.8) as it requires consideration of cultural and socioeconomic factors in patient care. It also maps moderately to PLO4 (0.5) and PLO5 (0.5).', '', '2026-02-20 13:34:37', '2026-02-20 13:34:37'),
(396, 44, 3, 10, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO4 (1.0) as it is explicitly about interpersonal and communication skills.', '', '2026-02-20 13:34:37', '2026-02-20 13:34:37'),
(397, 44, 3, 11, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO6 (1.0) as it requires knowledge of how local healthcare systems deliver patient care. It also maps strongly to PLO1 (0.8).', '', '2026-02-20 13:34:37', '2026-02-20 13:34:37'),
(398, 44, 4, 12, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO5 (0.8) as professionalism in the local context requires an understanding of Arabic-Islamic identity and values. It also maps moderately to PLO1 (0.5) and PLO4 (0.5).', '', '2026-02-20 13:34:37', '2026-02-20 13:34:37'),
(399, 44, 4, 13, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO1 (0.8), PLO4 (0.8), and PLO5 (0.8) as patient care, communication, and professionalism all require embracing diversity.', '', '2026-02-20 13:34:37', '2026-02-20 13:34:37'),
(400, 44, 4, 14, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO5 (1.0) as it is explicitly about ethics and professionalism.', '', '2026-02-20 13:34:37', '2026-02-20 13:34:37'),
(401, 44, 4, 15, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO1 (0.8) and PLO6 (1.0) as patient and population care and understanding healthcare systems are core aspects of civic engagement for a physician.', '', '2026-02-20 13:34:37', '2026-02-20 13:34:37'),
(402, 44, 5, 17, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO3 (0.8) as evidence-based practice and lifelong learning drive innovation in medicine. It also maps moderately to PLO1 (0.5), PLO2 (0.5), and PLO6 (0.5).', '', '2026-02-20 13:34:37', '2026-02-20 13:34:37'),
(403, 44, 5, 18, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO4 (1.0) as it is explicitly about working effectively in interprofessional groups.', '', '2026-02-20 13:34:37', '2026-02-20 13:34:37'),
(404, 44, 5, 19, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO1 (0.8) and PLO6 (1.0) as formulating management strategies and understanding healthcare systems are management functions.', '', '2026-02-20 13:34:37', '2026-02-20 13:34:37'),
(405, 44, 5, 20, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO4 (1.0) as it is explicitly about interpersonal and communication skills. It also maps strongly to PLO5 (0.8).', '', '2026-02-20 13:34:37', '2026-02-20 13:34:37'),
(406, 44, 5, 21, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO4 (0.8) and PLO6 (0.8) as working in complex healthcare systems and making decisions for groups provide opportunities for leadership.', '', '2026-02-20 13:34:37', '2026-02-20 13:34:37'),
(407, 43, 1, 1, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO6 (1.0) as it is explicitly about being a medication therapy expert. It also maps strongly to PLO1 (0.8) as providing pharmaceutical care requires deep subject matter knowledge.', '', '2026-02-20 13:35:52', '2026-02-20 10:36:45'),
(408, 43, 1, 2, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO1 (0.8) and PLO6 (0.8) as both care provision and scholarship require significant critical thinking. It also maps moderately across PLO2, PLO3, PLO4, PLO5, and PLO7 (0.5).', '', '2026-02-20 13:35:52', '2026-02-20 10:36:45'),
(409, 43, 1, 3, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO1 (1.0) as it is explicitly about providing pharmaceutical care and managing patient�s medication needs, which is a core problem-solving activity. It also maps strongly to PLO4 (0.8), PLO5 (0.8), and PLO6 (0.8).', '', '2026-02-20 13:35:52', '2026-02-20 10:36:45'),
(410, 43, 1, 4, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO6 (1.0) as it is explicitly about mastering, generating, interpreting and disseminating pharmaceutical and pharmacy practice knowledge.', '', '2026-02-20 13:35:52', '2026-02-20 10:36:45'),
(411, 43, 2, 5, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO7 (0.8) as being a self-regulated professional includes recognizing one\'s own limitations and continuously improving. It also maps moderately to PLO1 (0.5), PLO4 (0.5), and PLO6 (0.5).', '', '2026-02-20 13:35:52', '2026-02-20 10:36:45'),
(412, 43, 2, 6, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO6 (0.8) and PLO7 (0.8) as scholarship and professionalism are the keys to adaptability in the pharmacy field. It also maps moderately across PLO1, PLO2, PLO3, PLO4, and PLO5 (0.5).', '', '2026-02-20 13:35:52', '2026-02-20 10:36:45'),
(413, 43, 2, 7, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO1 (0.8) and PLO6 (0.8) as both care provision and scholarship require adaptive thinking to respond to new information and patient conditions.', '', '2026-02-20 13:35:52', '2026-02-20 10:36:45'),
(414, 43, 2, 8, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO6 (1.0) as it is explicitly about scholarship and lifelong learning.', '', '2026-02-20 13:35:52', '2026-02-20 10:36:45'),
(415, 43, 3, 9, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO1 (0.5), PLO2 (0.5), PLO3 (0.5), PLO5 (0.5), and PLO7 (0.5) as providing care to diverse audiences requires cultural awareness.', '', '2026-02-20 13:35:52', '2026-02-20 10:36:45'),
(416, 43, 3, 10, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO2 (1.0) as it is explicitly about communication. It also maps strongly to PLO3 (0.8).', '', '2026-02-20 13:35:52', '2026-02-20 10:36:45'),
(417, 43, 3, 11, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO5 (1.0) as being a health advocate requires awareness of local and international issues. It also maps moderately to PLO1 (0.5), PLO3 (0.5), and PLO7 (0.5).', '', '2026-02-20 13:35:52', '2026-02-20 10:36:45'),
