(422, 43, 5, 17, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO6 (0.8) as scholarship drives innovation in pharmacy. It also maps moderately to PLO1 (0.5), PLO4 (0.5), and PLO5 (0.5).', '', '2026-02-20 13:35:52', '2026-02-20 10:36:45'),
