(424, 43, 5, 19, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO4 (1.0) as it is explicitly about being a leader/manager. It also maps strongly to PLO1 (0.8).', '', '2026-02-20 13:35:52', '2026-02-20 10:36:45'),
