(429, 46, 1, 3, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO2 (1.0) and PLO5 (1.0) as providing patient-centered care and integrating evidence-based practice are core problem-solving activities. It also maps strongly to PLO1 (0.8), PLO7 (0.8), and PLO8 (0.8).', '', '2026-02-20 13:37:10', '2026-02-20 13:37:10'),
(430, 46, 1, 4, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO5 (1.0) as evidence-based practice requires research skills. It also maps strongly to PLO1 (0.8).', '', '2026-02-20 13:37:10', '2026-02-20 13:37:10'),
(431, 46, 2, 5, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO4 (0.8) as assuming responsibility for professional standards includes self-awareness.', '', '2026-02-20 13:37:10', '2026-02-20 13:37:10'),
