(442, 46, 5, 17, 'This competency is most strongly mapped to PLO2 (0.8), PLO5 (0.8), PLO6 (0.8), and PLO7 (0.8) as patient care, evidence-based practice, technology use, and leadership all drive innovation in nursing.', '', '2026-02-20 13:37:10', '2026-02-20 13:37:10'),
